{"tid":2340194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"智能門鈴變偷窺系統 亞馬遜遭索償","createTime":"2020-12-25T09:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T09:22:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cbf04a1730b533ed3bf4ebe73858ec21708aedde","tid":2340194,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:01:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201225/VFL6KDCLDJETPJHLYNMMWHMNEQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201225%2FVFL6KDCLDJETPJHLYNMMWHMNEQ%2F&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=cb73cee5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201225%2FVFL6KDCLDJETPJHLYNMMWHMNEQ%2F&h=12375beb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201225/VFL6KDCLDJETPJHLYNMMWHMNEQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n智能門鈴變偷窺系統 亞馬遜遭索償<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lgo4qCzjKfX1bCpVSY3JGR3RrUg=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VFL3FRKPKVGQVK2PCJMBPUJQP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Flgo4qCzjKfX1bCpVSY3JGR3RrUg%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVFL3FRKPKVGQVK2PCJMBPUJQP4.jpg&h=3dbd5e12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Ring保安系統在門鈴和室內都有鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜網站自家推售的智能門鈴與家居保安系統Ring揭出保安問題，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拒更新被斥卸責<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。，令歹徒有機可乘，防盜系統反成私隱盡失的偷窺系統。<br />\n<br />\n案情指有住戶為獨居婆婆裝設系統，方便遙距看顧，歹徒用系統虐嚇老人，向對講機大叫：「今晚你死定了！」嚇得婆婆搬走。又有歹徒入侵系統播恐怖片配樂作弄某戶三個小孩，其中患癲癎四歲幼女受驚病發可致命，令戶主辭工留家。<br />\n<br />\n受害人又說，他們向Ring報告後，久久才有空泛回應，。。。。。。。。。。，指2015年至去年全部用家都有權向亞馬遜索償。<br />\n<br />\n英國《衞報》"},{"pid":"107679bd1add8e2cce75d27c693195dabd9c1803","tid":2340194,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"個呀婆好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd331dba8baabb5a5832dd719ce00e7058672c5","tid":2340194,"uid":263025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"老人家比人入屋點搞都無得反抗。<br />\n<br />\n如果無同後生住"},{"pid":"d005ba9e240313902d2ad087a0f93ec804c39524","tid":2340194,"uid":364850,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:12:40.000Z","msg":"嘩屌  差啲殺死個細女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a46370d4e972ffb31c1ebe1ea2c631353e258b","tid":2340194,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:13:46.000Z","msg":"出發點係好<br />\n但舊垃圾整得唔好"},{"pid":"a15b0820e539ca51eb5614150f1c653869f7efee","tid":2340194,"uid":154054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:17:05.000Z","msg":"好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇咁無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432fedb99e2ffcadfe0f8cf099d50e625b1c4474","tid":2340194,"uid":21732,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:19:21.000Z","msg":"「公司更推卸責任給用戶，指是他們的密碼設防太低太簡單，沒有按建議設定更複雜的密碼和輸入電話等進行雙重認證。」<br />\n<br />\npassword set constraint 同一定要你開雙重記證有幾難<br />\n<br />\n用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4b65e385162416246a2398e82311f2aa70b149","tid":2340194,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"432fedb99e2ffcadfe0f8cf099d50e625b1c4474","tid":2340194,"uid":21732,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:19:21.000Z","msg":"「公司更推卸責任給用戶，指是他們的密碼設防太低太簡單，沒有按建議設定更複雜的密碼和輸入電話等進行雙重認證。」<br />\n<br